🔄 Automated Data Comparison
Compare datasets (Excel/CSV) to detect added, deleted, and modified records using key-based matching.
🧠 Smart Change Detection Logic
Identifies changes only across shared columns and highlights exact differences using a clear “old → new” format
📊 Excel Report Generation (Wide Format)
Automatically generates structured Excel reports with:
Changed cells highlighted (yellow)
New rows (green)
Deleted rows (red)
New columns (blue)
📧 Outlook Email Draft Automation
Creates ready-to-send email drafts including:
Summary of detected changes
Embedded screenshots
Attached Excel reports
🖼️ Visual Reporting (Image Snapshots)
Generates visual summaries of dataset changes for easy review by stakeholders.
📁 Automatic File Detection
Detects latest dataset files based on naming patterns (e.g., dataset_YYYY-MM-DD.xlsx) to streamline daily workflows.
⚙️ Multi-Dataset Processing
Supports multiple datasets in a single run with configurable keys and comparison modes.
🎛️ User-Friendly GUI
Interactive interface built with Tkinter for:
File selection
Key selection
Mode configuration
Process monitoring
📦 Consolidated Reporting
Combines multiple dataset comparisons into a single Excel workbook with separate sheets per dataset.
🔁 End-to-End Automation Workflow
Fully automates the process from:
data comparison → report generation → email draft creation
